Package mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.dimension

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DimensionField<T extends CommonIndexValue>
    This interface provides in addition to the index dimension definition, a way to read and write a field and get a field ID
    Time
    The base interface for time values, could be either a time range (an interval) or a timestamp (an instant)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeometryAdapter
    This adapter can be used for reading and writing Geometry fields within GeoWave.
    GeometryWrapper
    This class wraps JTS geometry with visibility so that it can be used within GeoWave as a CommonIndexValue
    LatitudeField
    This field can be used as a EPSG:4326 latitude dimension within GeoWave.
    LongitudeField
    This field can be used as a EPSG:4326 longitude dimension within GeoWave.
    SpatialField
    A base class for EPSG:4326 latitude/longitude fields that use JTS geometry
    Time.TimeRange
    A range of time.
    Time.Timestamp
    An instant of time in milliseconds wrapped with a visibility tag for the field value.
    TimeAdapter
    This adapter can be used for reading and writing Time fields within GeoWave and enables a temporal field definition.
    TimeField
    This field definition can be used for temporal data (either as a time range or a single instant in time).
